description: My Granny’s Kitchen is the truck you want to visit if you’re looking for a more nutritious alternative to fast food, where you never have to sacrifice efficiency, quality, and home-style deliciousness. This soul cooking is sure to satisfy your comfort cravings, like the ultra-scrumptious Baked Chicken & Rice, Smothered Pork Chop, Meatloaf, with your choice of sides such as Macaroni & Cheese, Black-eyed Peas, Collard Greens, and so much more. For a meal that you can enjoy with your friends and family from start to finish, you’re always warmly invited to My Granny’s Kitchen.
name: My Granny's Kitchen
